  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785180/extras/4244bc0ba39fc1e8b3e27464e1e66789.poster.avif?t=1727700657\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785180/extras/4244bc0ba39fc1e8b3e27464e1e66789.webm?t=1727700657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785180/extras/4244bc0ba39fc1e8b3e27464e1e66789.mp4?t=1727700657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RAIN. RUNNER.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rain Runner is a short, blood-pumping speedrunning FPS where you ditch your keyboard and only use your mouse! You’ll run constantly where you look, shoot targets and dash through challenging platforms. No checkpoints, no pauses: beat it in one sitting! Run, die, learn, repeat. Be better, be faster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES.</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👟25 handcrafted, fast, and hard levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕘About 30mins gameplay (unlimited, if you're up for challenge)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️Steam Leaderboard (best player featured in the main menu *wow*)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎶An original soundtrack consisting of 6 tracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆Cool achievements!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💾NO saves and pauses, beat in one sitting!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☠️Annoying meta-dialogues</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785180/extras/284f235c7d2a4c0f9dd616a2444836af.avif?t=1727700657\" width=200 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Hi, it's SkyBrave! I make short games every month! Join my Discord channel to stay connected!</i></strong></p>",
